<subSubSection id="C368652E935F8E02F2AAF931FAF2F92A" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935F8E02F2AAF931FAF2F92A" blockId="6.[151,1437,1699,2014]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF8935F8E02F2AAF931FACEF92A" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147307" collectorName="J. Serrano" determinerName="Z. Mylnar" location="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" specimenCount="4" stateProvince="Sicilia" typeStatus="lectotype">
The 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F2F4F931FEE1F976" box="[201,304,1699,1725]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing labels “a male symbol, “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F139F931FC83F976" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[772,850,1699,1725]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siculus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F139F931FC83F976" box="[772,850,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">siculus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in 
<collectingRegion id="49B6F847935F8E02F1ABF931FC32F976" box="[918,995,1699,1725]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Sicilia</collectingRegion>
”, “Schüppel”, “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F6B2F931FAFAF976" box="[1167,1323,1699,1725]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">HOLOTYPE</typeStatus>
”, “vidit 
<determinerName id="7E11DA61935F8E02F7B9F936FF38F92A" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Z. Mylnář</determinerName>
det 1974”, “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F34BF955FDCDF92A" box="[374,540,1735,1761]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">LECTOTYPE</typeStatus>
” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F058F955FD01F92A" box="[613,720,1735,1761]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F0C8F955FB82F92A" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[757,1107,1735,1761]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siculus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F0C8F955FC65F92A" box="[757,948,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Harpalus siculus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F186F955FB82F92A" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[955,1107,1735,1761]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<collectorName id="26875373935F8E02F663F95AFB1FF92A" box="[1118,1230,1735,1762]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">J. Serrano</collectorName>
vidit.”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E935F8E02F2FAF979FB6CF816" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935F8E02F2FAF979FC7FF871" blockId="6.[151,1437,1699,2014]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">
The card stating 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F3BAF979FDF6F8CE" box="[391,551,1771,1797]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">LECTOTYPE</typeStatus>
was likely placed by Mylnář, but this is a mislabelling as the specimen is the 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F2AAF89DFF28F8E2" box="[151,249,1807,1833]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">holotype</typeStatus>
(see below). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F3B2F89DFDE1F8E2" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[399,560,1807,1833]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
briefly stated the origin of the specimen: 
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F63FF89DFB3AF8E2" box="[1026,1259,1807,1833]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">
Il se trouve en 
<collectingRegion id="49B6F847935F8E02F69BF89DFB39F8E2" box="[1190,1256,1807,1833]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Sicile</collectingRegion>
.
</emphasis>
From the original description it is inferred that he only could study a single specimen sent by M. Schüppel. Thus, this specimen becomes the 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F315F8C5FE5BF8BA" box="[296,394,1879,1905]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">holotype</typeStatus>
of the species by monotypy. Although Mylnář did not formally publish the recognition of this specimen as the 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935F8E02F369F8E9FE68F85E" box="[340,441,1915,1941]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">holotype</typeStatus>
, it is clear from the label that he recognized the type condition of the specimen he saw. Keys to the species are available in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F015F832FD14F872" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[552,709,1951,1978]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente (1927)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F0C7F80DFC78F871" author="Antoine, M." box="[762,937,1951,1978]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine (1959)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935F8E02F2FAF856FB6CF816" blockId="6.[151,1437,1699,2014]" box="[199,1213,1987,2014]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">
To date the species is known from 
<collectingCountry id="F3657635935F8E02F071F851FD51F816" box="[588,640,1987,2013]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Italy</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F3657635935F8E02F0B1F851FD1DF816" box="[652,716,1987,2013]" name="Spain" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">Spain</collectingCountry>
and the Maghreb (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F1A2F851FB61F816" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[927,1200,1987,2014]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
